snippet.title: Amber Heard getting over divorce with Margot Robbie, fine dining
snippet.description:
Amber Heard got after it with Margot Robbie and others in London following the same day her divorce with Johnny Depp was finalized. F-R-E-E-D-O-M never felt so damn good.
